Package: iSEEfier
Title: Create an initial state of an iSEE instance to visualize RNA-seq data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Najla", "Abassi", , "najla.abassi@uni-mainz.de", role = c("cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8357-0938"))
Description: Enhance the visualization of gene expression in RNA-seq data using iSEE, making it more intuitive and straightforward by creating various initial states. This will save time defining the appropriate panels and settings from a default iSEE instance.
